                        <interp inst="t18400106-name-404" type="given" value="JOHN GYLES"></interp>JOHN GYLES HALES.</persName>
                  </hi>I am a pawnbroker. I produce this coat, pawned by the prisoner on the 27th of December.</p>
               <p>
